    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A sport in which two opponents grapple with each other in order to force the other to touch the ground with a part of the body other than the feet, or into a supine position for some amount of time. The term encompasses various styles.</Note_Text>
